Contributing to pxweb R packge

Source: CONTRIBUTING.md

You are welcome to contact us:

  • Submit suggestions and bug reports (provide the output of sessionInfo() and packageVersion("pxweb"))
  • Send a pull request
  • Star us on the Github page
  • Join the discussion in Gitter

Acknowledgements

Kindly cite this work as follows: Måns Magnusson, Markus Kainu, Janne Huovari, and Leo Lahti. Retrieval and analysis of PC Axis data with the pxweb package. R package version r sessionInfo()$otherPkgs$pxweb$Version. URL: http://ropengov.github.io/pxweb

We are grateful to all contributors! This project is part of rOpenGov.
